TO set a var value in terraform you can use 
1. terraform.tfvars file
2. env var "it's name is " TF_VAR_<varname>
3. using cli -var key=value option
4. prompt 
5. default value
6. -var-file 
cli => env var => terraform.tfvars *.auto.tfvars => default => prompt


To reference attribute of a resource
<resource_type>.<resource_name>.<attribute_name>

depends_on meta-arguement makes an explicit denpendency between resources
if a resource references another resources this makes implict dependency between the resources